name: Famished Frog
description:
• W - Jump / Swim Up
  • A - Move Left
  • S - Move Down
  • D - Move Right

Help this Famished Frog find food! Eat as much as you can within the 1 min 30 s and try to get the highest score! Beware of the evil big fishes! They will steal your points and take away your time!

Experience the game better by downloading the game exe.
